												| Never in all their history have men been able truly to conceive of the world as one: a single sphere, a globe, having the qualities of a globe, a round earth in which all the directions eventually meet, in which there is no center.

										// add
										.add
											span
												a( href="#" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Drag your media here" )
													img( src="img/ui/ic-add.png" )

